Project Name: Student Performance Prediction

This project predicts student math scores using machine learning techniques.

01.Dataset
StudentsPerformance.csv

02.Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn

03. Machine Learning Models
- Linear Regression
- Random Forest

04.Evaluation Metrics
- RMSE
- R² Score

05.Key Insights
Reading and writing scores strongly influence math score prediction.

06.Visualizations
- Distribution of Math Scores
- Correlation Heatmap
- Feature Importance
- Actual vs Predicted Plot
